data.description: Welcome home to this exquisite 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom Florentine Model Home situated on a coveted corner lot in the highly sought-after Tuscany development. With an array of remarkable features and breathtaking mountain and desert views, this property offers a truly exceptional living experience,. This homes  includes an attached casita with a full bath and a separate front entrance, providing flexibility for guests, in-laws, or a home office. inside, discover the timeless elegance of travertine marble floors that grace the 2,803 sq. ft. of living space. The spacious living room and private dining room boast impressive 10-foot ceilings and a convenient wet bar.The open kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring granite countertops, a butler's pantry, a large center island with a breakfast counter. Adjacent to the kitchen, a generous family/TV room with a cozy fireplace awaits family gatherings and entertainment. Modern living is made easy with  washer/dryer in the separate laundry room.  Two guest rooms, one with an ensuite hall bath, offer comfort and privacy. The grand master bedroom features a spacious walk-in closet and a beautifully appointed master bath, complete with a jacuzzi tub, and a luxurious glass block walk-in shower. This home also includes a leased SOLAR  with SUNPOWER AT $225/month The three-car garage ,and plenty of storage! Step outside to your private oasis, where you'll find a new, highly upgraded pool and spa ! HOA includes cable and internet.
